{"tid":813342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到完場】歐美氣象電腦預測有颱風下周吹襲香港　天文台料港風力僅清勁級別","createTime":"2018-09-10T11:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T11:10:47.000Z","uid":56982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a35cb483c1fddd3ec0f83ff662109def69540bd","tid":813342,"uid":56982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"6-9-2018<br />\n<br />\n踏入秋季，今秋第一股東北季候風在周末南下之際，同時將有一個熱帶氣旋或會緊接吹襲台灣至香港所在的南海北部。美國全球預報系統（GFS）預測該熱帶氣旋先於下周初靠近台灣東南部，再向西移，下周中正面吹襲本港，甚至有可能在香港登陸；歐洲中期天氣預報中心（ECMWF）電腦預測也相似，但料只會在香港南面近距離掠過，但破壞力也不可小覷。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天文台指該低壓區會在下周初至中期，為台灣至南海北部一帶帶來不穩定天氣，但預料下周本港最大風力只達5級，僅屬清勁級別。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，歐美預報顯示，將有另一熱帶氣旋於下周末迫近台灣，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天文台就指熱帶氣旋向未形成，各預報系統的分歧較大。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/232249/%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E6%9C%89%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%90%B9%E8%A5%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E6%96%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A2%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%83%85%E6%B8%85%E5%8B%81%E7%B4%9A%E5%88%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F232249%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2590%25B9%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%2583%2585%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%258B%2581%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%2588%25A5&d=cE8iLJcogGCGUKmxDnImtI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=652566ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/232249/%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E6%9C%89%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%90%B9%E8%A5%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E6%96%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A2%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%83%85%E6%B8%85%E5%8B%81%E7%B4%9A%E5%88%A5</a>"},{"pid":"610295d10c8cff7f4e74d2f78dfd87002cddddfc","tid":813342,"uid":100550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"有力場<br />\n有大交合<br />\n星期一 <br />\n<br />\n最多三號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時記得準時番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}